<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 9:49 AM EST, Thu January 16, 2014
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
<a href="/2014/01/15/sport/football/poland-football-anti-semitism/index.html?iid=article_sidebar"><img src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/140115153202-poznan-tease-video-tease.jpg" alt="" border="0" height="68" width="120"/></a>
</div>
